    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Along the way of TWA...\nSPHINX AND PYRAMIDS\nCairo\nThe ancient,\nfabled Sphinx and\nthe Pyramids were built\nby the Pharaohs\nthousands of years ago.\nYou will see them\nas you fly to Cairo,\nAfrica's largest city,\nin TWA's swift,\nmodern Skyliners.\nTWA\nTRANS WORLD AIRLINES\nU.S. A. • EUROPE\nAFRICA ASIA",
